==English==
===Noun===
'''bleach''' (''[[uncountable]] and [[countable]]''; ''plural'' '''bleaches''')

# {{uncountable}} A chemical, such as [[sodium hypochlorite]] or [[hydrogen peroxide]], or a preparation of such a chemical, used for [[disinfect]]ing or [[whiten]]ing; (''[[countable]]'') a variety of bleach.

