===Transitive verb===
'''to bleach''' (''[[present participle]]'' '''bleaching''', ''[[past tense]] and [[past participle]]'' '''bleached''')

#To treat with bleach, especially so as to [[whiten]] (fabric, paper, etc) or [[lighten]] (hair).

